snippet.title: Mixolumia - Rush Mode Gameplay (with music by Josie Brechner)
snippet.description:
Mixolumia introduces a fresh twist on block-clearing puzzlers. Scintillating visuals and entrancing music respond to your input and evolve as you progress. Diamond blocks slide together on the gem-shaped board, enabling you to set up chain reactions and earn high-scoring combos.

Visit http://www.mixolumia.com for more
